sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Command as Cloud Research Command
    participant Task as Task Tool
    participant Agent as Research Agent
    participant MCP as MCP Server
    participant Web as WebSearch/WebFetch
    participant FS as File System
    
    User->>Command: /arckit.aws-research Analyze AWS Lambda vs ECS
    Command->>Task: Delegate to arckit-aws-research agent
    Task->>Agent: Spawn subprocess with research query
    
    Agent->>Agent: Parse requirements from project artifacts
    Agent->>Agent: Extract required AWS services
    
    Agent->>MCP: Query AWS Lambda documentation
    MCP-->>Agent: Service docs, best practices, limits
    Agent->>MCP: Query AWS ECS documentation
    MCP-->>Agent: Service docs, architecture patterns
    
    Agent->>Web: Search "AWS Lambda pricing calculator"
    Web-->>Agent: Pricing data, TCO examples
    Agent->>Web: Search "AWS Lambda vs ECS reddit"
    Web-->>Agent: Customer experiences, gotchas
    
    Agent->>Agent: Synthesize findings into research doc
    Agent->>Agent: Extract vendor profile data
    
    Agent->>FS: Write research/ARC-001-AWRS-001-v1.0.md
    Agent->>FS: Write vendors/aws-profile.md
    Agent->>FS: Write tech-notes/serverless-comparison.md
    
    Agent-->>Task: Research complete with file paths
    Task-->>Command: Agent output
    Command-->>User: Summary with artifact links
